init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And then you just stand there.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Because you have no idea how to make yourself suddenly be #1.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Is there anyone in the world that you can bribe to make them tell you where they ranked, or what their ranking was?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You open the package and see that the mug lists your neighbor in at #4.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But you are afraid that someone might hear, so you run to the back yard and fling it as hard as you can over the fence into the

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are the #4 ranked dad in the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The box is floating in the water, so you reach down into the pond and retrieve it.
